flowchart TD
    A([User Input\nImage / Audio / Text]) --> B{Input Type}
    B -- Image --> C[OCR Tool\nGemini Vision]
    B -- Audio --> D[ASR Tool\nGemini Audio]
    B -- Text --> E[Text Input]

    C --> F[Extraction Preview\nUser can edit]
    D --> F
    E --> F

    F --> G[Parser Agent\nStructures problem]
    G -- needs_clarification=true --> H[[HITL Panel\nUser corrects]]
    H --> G

    G --> I[Router Agent\nClassifies + strategies]
    I --> J[RAG Retriever\nChromaDB KB]
    J --> K[Memory Retriever\nSQLite + Chroma]
    K --> L[Solver Agent\nGemini + Python Tool]

    L --> M[Verifier / Critic Agent]
    M -- is_correct=false AND retries < 2 --> L
    M -- hitl_required=true --> H
    M -- verified --> N[Explainer Agent\nStudent-friendly output]

    N --> O[Streamlit UI\nAnswer + Trace + Sources]
    O --> P{User Feedback}
    P -- correct --> Q[(Memory Store\nSQLite + Chroma)]
    P -- incorrect+comment --> Q
    Q -.->|Future retrieval| K
